name: UCommonSession_SearchSessionRequest
doc: Request object describing a session search, this object will be updated once the search has completed

OnlineMode: Indicates if the this is looking for full online games or a different type like LAN
bUseLobbies: True if this request should look for player-hosted lobbies if they are available, false will only search for registered server sessions
Results: List of all found sessions, will be valid when OnSearchFinished is called
K2_OnSearchFinished: Delegate called when a session search completes
